body: I was Wondering if there was a you-tuber rank, if so how many subscribers do i need to get a YT rank. I have 700+ Subscribers

title: Youtuber Rank?

replies.body: 20000+ Gives you the VIP Rank the only player that has it is Minkks. http://avicus.net/Minkks

replies.body:
You need 5000 subscribers  to get the VIP rank.
If you want the YouTuber rank, you need 50,000 subscribers.

Correct me if I'm wrong.
